[l] Russland tritt aus dem Internationalen Strafgerichtshof aus. Begruendung:The Russian Foreign Ministry said the ICC had "failed to meet the expectations to become a truly independent, authoritative international tribunal," in a statement released Wednesday.Tsja, das ist ja nun leider nicht voellig von der Hand zu weisen.It described the ICC as "ineffective," adding that "during the 14 years of the court's work it passed only four sentences having spent over a billion dollars."Auch das klingt wie valide Kritik. Aber ihr kennt das ja, man hat zwei vorgeschobene Gruende, und dann hat man den eigentlichen Grund. So ist das auch hier:Russia also criticized the court's handling of the country's five-day conflict with neighboring Georgia in 2008, saying "we can hardly trust the ICC in such a situation."
